content.rendered:
The Country Round Ottoman is similar to our standard Chunk Ottman but with Country fabrics and faux leathers. 

Often paired with our leather sofas for a warm, cosy feel in your restaurant, café, pub or bar.

This item comes with a 6 month guarantee
